[A check of The Cape Times shows no prior reports of this disease since 2011. And OIE has no South African notifications for 2013 that I could find. Would someone please update us on the actual situation in South Africa for African horse sickness outbreaks? This Western Cape report says there have been 208 cases elsewhere in the country with some 60 percent case fatality rate. - Mod.MHJ]

